{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"1mt5am4uwnvwb6oeym9weke","title":"Polybar","desc":"","updated":1661057661573,"created":1661056377835,"custom":{},"fname":"linux.customization.polybar","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"117b02b6a54898c31c8beabc6f693362","links":[{"from":{"fname":"linux.customization.install-checklist","id":"6heqjju0cm02y0rjgk9kajk","vaultName":"docs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":7,"offset":327},"end":{"line":13,"column":38,"offset":358},"indent":[]},"value":"linux.customization.polybar"}],"anchors":{"polybar-is-customizable-status-bar-integrate-with-i3":{"type":"header","text":"polybar is customizable status bar, integrate with i3","value":"polybar-is-customizable-status-bar-integrate-with-i3","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"install":{"type":"header","text":"install","value":"install","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"config":{"type":"header","text":"config","value":"config","line":40,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"0dcz8bz1ladgjebaljq61w7","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"polybar\">Polybar<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#polybar\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"polybar-is-customizable-status-bar-integrate-with-i3\">polybar is customizable status bar, integrate with i3<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#polybar-is-customizable-status-bar-integrate-with-i3\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/polybar/polybar\">https://github.com/polybar/polybar</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"install\">install<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#install\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>command <code>sudo apt install polybar</code> -> <strong>unable to locate</strong></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/polybar/polybar/wiki/Compiling\">Compile</a>\n<ul>\n<li>Dependencies (apt)\n<pre><code>sudo apt install -y build-essential git cmake cmake-data pkg-config python3-sphinx python3-packaging libuv1-dev libcairo2-dev libxcb1-dev libxcb-util0-dev libxcb-randr0-dev libxcb-composite0-dev python3-xcbgen xcb-proto libxcb-image0-dev libxcb-ewmh-dev libxcb-icccm4-dev\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code>sudo apt install -y libxcb-xkb-dev libxcb-xrm-dev libxcb-cursor-dev libasound2-dev libpulse-dev i3-wm libjsoncpp-dev libmpdclient-dev libcurl4-openssl-dev libnl-genl-3-dev\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Compiling\n<ul>\n<li>clone the repo <a href=\"https://github.com/polybar/polybar\">https://github.com/polybar/polybar</a> (have to clone all <strong>submodules</strong>)\n<code>git clone --recursive https://github.com/polybar/polybar</code></li>\n<li>cd to the folder</li>\n<li>run\n<pre><code>mkdir build\ncd build\ncmake ..\nmake -j$(nproc)\n# Optional. This will install the polybar executable in /usr/local/bin\nsudo make install\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>error\n<ul>\n<li>/home/thanhpp/github.com/polybar/polybar/lib/xpp does not contain a CMakeLists.txt file. Target xpp not generated</li>\n<li>Didn't clone submodules -> missing file</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"config\">config<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#config\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>placed in <code>$HOME/.config/polybar</code></li>\n<li>soft link</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/6heqjju0cm02y0rjgk9kajk\">Install Checklist</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron",